Title: Weekly: Stab em up
Descriptions: Listen close, 'cause Rico's laying down the law. I'm not here to mince words. I'm here to set the record straight: 100 knife kills. That's right. 100. No guns, no fancy tricks. Just you, your blade, and the grit to get it done. You want rewards? You want respect? Then you gotta prove you're tough as nails. You gotta show me you got what it takes to survive in this dog-eat-dog world. Survivors, this ain't for the faint-hearted. This is for the ones who ain't afraid to get their hands dirty, who ain't afraid to stare death in the eye and laugh. So strap up, sharpen your blades, and get ready to hunt. Because in this world, it's kill or be killed. And only the strong will survive. Rico, out.
